{"tid":1955263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解最近有咁多單外地輸入","createTime":"2020-04-02T11:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T11:42:16.000Z","uid":159819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"169a8a7043d52a15b63345d46c0f9ab335983bc2","tid":1955263,"uid":159819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:07:29.000Z","msg":"最近睇新聞一直都唔明點解外國輸入既個案會咁高。明明全世界都知支那漏報，個真實感染人數應該點都幾十萬，港共又唔肯封關，香港人都係守住百幾宗就停左。<br />\n<br />\n但一到歐洲美國爆，香港日日外地傳入都幾十宗，三月中到依家眨下眼就升撚到六百宗。<br />\n<br />\n到底點解會咁，明明支那瞞報既數字應該多過歐美，但兩個時期外地輸入香港既個案差成三四倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKocQRi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKocQRi.png&h=87e90b68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8764da4714e722b460d7156b51d3f9b6aa29a861","tid":1955263,"uid":159819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:11:55.000Z","msg":"支那可摸耳快d爆第二波，唔想獎牌榜比西班牙都過埋頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11e6202f2d0e5739ccb13547cf79b66d178a1e4","tid":1955263,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"因為大陸入嚟唔驗囉"},{"pid":"fb7b3b196ad02b2e04c40dc1278037a0e928eaef","tid":1955263,"uid":159819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a11e6202f2d0e5739ccb13547cf79b66d178a1e4","tid":1955263,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"因為大陸入嚟唔驗囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"兩邊唔係都強制檢疫十四日咩，有咩分別？"}]}